id: pm-b4cp
title: "Audit (2026-06-07): MCP + SDK/extensions/packages"
description: "Audit session covering src/mcp/server.ts, src/sdk/, src/core/extensions/, src/core/packages/, and packages/pm-*. Goal: identify genuine forward-backlog gaps in MCP protocol coverage, SDK surface, extension capabilities, package platform, and first-party exemplars."
